        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 12.— Kujdanowiaspis podolica (Brotzen,1934):skull roof reconstruction (dorsal view);the right half takes the perspective into account (head down and lateral portion curved down). Drawing by Agathe Ravet (MNHN). Abbreviations: see Appendix 2. Scale bar: 1 cm." ;
